::Kluster::

Kluster nods, tapping a few keys to see the background of the bot. He 
had been captured doing an infultration of the Cybertronian Fire, so 
he might know some security things that were otherwise secret.

"I'm sorry," Kluster replies, "But he would have to be put through a 
scan to see if he knows anything that could put the Cybertronian Fire 
and the Maximals into further danger. Do you mind if we scan him?"
